2.3 Training Algorithm
The training algorithm of MINILLM is shown in Algorithm 2.3. We initialize the student model from a checkpoint fine-tuned on the training data with the lowest validation loss and add the PPO clipping strategy [SWD+17] to (‚àáJ )Main to improve training stability. Note that we do not use the value network and the KL regularization in PPO to improve the training efficiency. Same as [OWJ+22], we add a language modeling loss LPT on the pre-training corpus.

